	<h1 class="title">宜家创始人说这么多年来，他的衣服都是二手市场买来的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马宁忆 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-11 07:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23657/medium/23657.jpg?1457612870" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="23657" data-title="《宜家创始人说这么多年来，他的衣服都是二手市场买来的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23657/medium/23657.jpg?1457612870" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23657.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
